{"tid":2438932,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇兄弟返到公司唔即刻屙屎會令到自己成個人冇乜士氣做嘢？","createTime":"2021-03-09T01:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T03:13:27.000Z","uid":40930,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"429f552f4ad6e10adf70e32d107b1f761dd29616","tid":2438932,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:08:29.000Z","msg":"返工真係好撚攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/linguistic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做嚟做去都係嗰啲嘢，久而久之就會冇乜動力，仲要人晨咁早返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣邊會想做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係最近發現返到去屙轉屎先做嘢個人會有返動力少少，因為見到目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾自己身體認住返公屙屎好爽好正，出返嚟做嘢就會期待下個鐘再入去屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果然身體最誠實<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06246a990b598ee7545b90dbe4263cb75f49290","tid":2438932,"uid":392319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:15:57.000Z","msg":"向公司廁格覆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a5993eaba4ffe24cb653efc396da03d1d6061f1","tid":2438932,"uid":56546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:38:03.000Z","msg":"食完早餐上午痾一督<br />\n下午又痾一督<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0aeb0cd0763dc756c7728dcb91f4df5ba6b2371","tid":2438932,"uid":287107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T02:04:44.000Z","msg":"要痾，唔痾唔通係個位癩屎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3701d25aefd1f8bc8bb8b7779f15900dfbcac09","tid":2438932,"uid":64253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T02:33:05.000Z","msg":"食完早餐一定柯30分鐘屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b549f6fb2270b3e94cded1a32fe4c09d4cc7d6d","tid":2438932,"uid":381502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T03:13:27.000Z","msg":"已經同公司廁所完美結合咗<br />\n番屋企反而屙唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}